            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Deo Marti aram <lb n="2"/>Iulius Emeri<lb break="no" n="3"/>tus <expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> VIII <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustae</ex></expan> Severianae <lb n="5"/><del rend="erasure">Alexandrian[ae</del>] <lb n="6"/>exactus co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ularis</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>dedicatam <lb n="8"/>XIII <expan><abbr>K</abbr><ex>alendas</ex></expan> Maias <lb n="9"/>Maximo et <lb n="10"/>Aeliano co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan> <lb n="11"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>aetus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Inschriftträger: Altar oder Basis / Statuenbasis. Material- und Maßangabe nach lupa 27080. (B): CIL 13, 06738; ILS: Z. 1 (Ende): Arm(ogio?); Z. 7: dedicata.</p>
